summary: Adds a player home for badnit/assassin characters to the game close to vanilla fasion.
descriptionHtml:
[size=3]Hello. Ive wanted to make a shabby looking player home inside of a cave for my assassin character since i didnt find any that i like and now im sharing it with you. I just finished it and tried it out and there seems to be no problem.

[color=#f4cccc]Details:[/color]
There are no static items and there is no custom storage. It is as vanilla as it gets.

[color=#f4cccc]Features:[/color]
It has some weapon plaques and mannequins, some chests, workbenches, a cooking station and more.

[color=#f4cccc]Location:[/color]
You can find it near the Pelagius Farm in Whiterun. If you fast travel there and look south, you should see a new Cave marker on your radar. Head there to discover it.[/size]
author: Alex
